{"tid":1386350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好被嚇怕","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:07:29.000Z","uid":34047,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93a91b01b3ac7debe87f537781eb3f041800a2a2","tid":1386350,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156518115656009&amp;id=747381008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156518115656009%26id%3D747381008&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=cf34faa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156518115656009&amp;id=747381008</a><br />\n<br />\n政權同軍警正在不斷咁提升散播恐懼，目標唔係嚇最勇嘅嗰班前線(因為根本嚇唔到)，而係佔多數嘅和理非示威者，「再出嚟就隨時連你哋都打埋」。<br />\n如果和理非群眾減退，前線年輕人變成「少數人」，抗爭嘅能量就會因為失去咗「民意喺我哋呢邊」呢個image而消亡。<br />\n和理非群眾係一個重大後盾，你可以想像成，每一個走出嚟嘅黑衫身影，都係一件精神上嘅救命「物資」。<br />\n所以唔好厭倦唔好退縮，唔好覺得無份/無能力做實質前線嘢自己就無用，每一個遊行集會都盡力去，要一次又一次咁在現場visible，數人頭。<br />\n堅持呀，霞姨。"},{"pid":"9c6cb774031af4b8d703aac84eb5b82cdc6ba67a","tid":1386350,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1334773b109bbd2c08a5b1c9bdeb1c87cbecc6c7","tid":1386350,"uid":59816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cd0a3681260c159be7790e053a8eb73d6018382","tid":1386350,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48c0bfc74b00b0a9453868764630b8ba1817e77","tid":1386350,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c5e1bcd6acd83eba7ec5e60a46c6f795b34a95","tid":1386350,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:58:57.0